<appendix id="app.changes">
  <title>Changes</title>
  <para>Find a list of changes of the style guide over its previous version
    below.
  </para>
  <!-- Use simple past. Prepend new versions to the beginning of the list. -->

  <sect1 id="sec.changes.q4.2013">
    <title>January 2013 Release</title>

    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>Restructured large parts of the Style Guide</para>
        <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>Removed <emphasis>Creating a Consistent Structure: Lessons
              for Lizards</emphasis> section.
            </para>
          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>Renamed <emphasis>Creating a Consistent Structure: Official
              SUSE Manuals</emphasis> to
              <emphasis>Outline of a Manual</emphasis>. Promoted
              <emphasis>Outline of a Manual</emphasis> to a
              <sgmltag>sect1</sgmltag>.
            </para>
          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>Split <emphasis>Writing and Editing</emphasis> into
              <xref linkend="sec.language"/> and
              <xref linkend="sec.structure.markup"/> and moved its subsections
              where they fit best. Moved <xref linkend="sec.procedure"/>
              (formerly <emphasis>Creating Procedures</emphasis>)
              and <xref linkend="sec.computerelement"/> (formerly
              <emphasis>Presenting Computer Elements</emphasis>) as
              subsections into <xref linkend="sec.structure.markup"/>.
            </para>
          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>Renamed <emphasis>Discriminatory Language</emphasis> to
              <xref linkend="sec.bias"/>.
            </para>
          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>Created <xref linkend="sec.manage"/> and moved
              <xref linkend="sec.remark"/>, <xref linkend="sec.xmlcomment"/>,
              and <xref linkend="sec.entity"/> as subsections into it.
            </para>
          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>Renamed <emphasis>Spelling Terms</emphasis> to
              <xref linkend="app.terminology"/> moved it into an appendix.
            </para>
          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>Outsourced <xref linkend="app.terminology"/>,
              <xref linkend="app.markup"/> into separate DocBook files.
            </para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Added this list of changes as a separate file.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Added list of authors.
        </para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para>Updated Legal Notice to refer to SUSE, LLC instead of
          Novell, Inc.
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

  </sect1>
</appendix>